1 twelve thousand or greater who are serving in office on the effective date of this Act shall
2 conclude their terms on January 1, 2027, except for those legislative body members of
3 cities with populations of twelve thousand or greater who were appointed less than three
4 months prior to the regular November election in 2026 pursuant to Section 152 of the
5 Constitution of Kentucky. Individuals appointed this way shall conclude their on January
6 1, 2030. The term of legislative body members of cities with populations of twelve
7 thousand or greater elected on and after the regular November election in 2026 shall be
8 for four years.
